cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SD 

The paper deals with neural models for semi-supervised learning, specifically in the context of domain shift. This falls under the broad category of machine learning (cs.LG) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also involves techniques related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and software engineering (cs.SD) for implementing and evaluating the models.
